<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.1.10">
<l>mūva rākiya voruvaṉai mūvula kuṇṭumiḻn taḷantāṉai</l>
<l>tēvar tāṉavar ceṉṟuceṉ ṟiṟaiñca<supplied>t</supplied>taṇ  tiruvayin tirapurattu</l>
<l>mēvu cōtiyai vēlvala vaṉkali kaṉṟivi ritturaitta</l>
<l>pāvu taṇṭamiḻ pattivai pāṭiṭap pāvaṅkaḷ payilāvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Sins will not remain when [one] finishes singing these ten [songs]</l>
<l rend="indent">in pervasive, graceful Tamil,</l>
<l>Composed by Kalikaṉṟi, skilled with the spear, elaborating on the light</l>
<l rend="indent">which abides in cool Tiruvayintirapuram,</l>
<l>As deva-s and dānava-s, arriving continuously, worship</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who became three,</l>
<l>The one who measured the three worlds,</l>
<l rend="indent">having consumed [and] spewed [them out again].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
